OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782319683
OL,3,CTwo-thirds of surveyed Channel
OL,4,CIslanders want UK's under-16s social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FWhen it comes to age, support grew
OL,8,Fwith older generations, with the
OL,9,Fmajority of Gen Z respondents (aged
OL,10,Fbetween 16 and 24 years) answering
OL,11,Fthat they would be against a social
OL,12,Fmedia ban for under-16s.
OL,14,FThose opposing the ban cited that
OL,15,Fchildren could easily bypass
OL,16,Frestrictions by lying about their age
OL,17,For using VPNs to conceal their online
OL,18,Fidentity.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
