FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1782319683
OL,3,CTwo-thirds of surveyed Channel
OL,4,CIslanders want UK's under-16s social
OL,5,Cmedia ban
OL,7,FThey also had concerns over the loss
OL,8,Fof privacy by requiring age
OL,9,Fverifications, a loss of digital
OL,10,Feducational tools such as YouTube
OL,11,Fvideos, and a lack of focus on holding
OL,12,Ftech companies to account.
OL,14,FPreferred alternative solutions
OL,15,Fincluded partial restrictions, such as
OL,16,Fat school or for those under 16, and
OL,17,Fteaching children to be more digitally
OL,18,Fliterate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
